Package: tspl-cups-driver
Version: @VER@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Run The Wall <hello@constly.com>
Depends: cups
Conflicts: hzd950-cups-driver
Replaces: hzd950-cups-driver
Provides: hzd950-cups-driver
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/RunTheWall/tspl-cups-driver
Description: Free CUPS driver for TSPL/TSPL2 thermal label printers
 A CUPS raster->TSPL driver for cheap USB TSPL thermal label printers (HZD950,
 Munbyn, iDPRT, HPRT and friends) for Linux / Raspberry Pi and beyond.
 Builds from source, so it runs on any CPU the vendor's x86-only driver won't.
